WEBVTT

00:02:59.545 --> 00:03:01.403
shule 25

00:03:01.427 --> 00:03:06.129
na karibia uniti 60000 za nyumba kila siku,

00:03:06.153 --> 00:03:07.443
kila siku

00:03:10.039 --> 00:03:12.911
Tutawezaje kujenga hivi vyote?

00:03:13.698 --> 00:03:18.055
Je tutafwata mfano wa ujenzi usio salama

00:03:18.079 --> 00:03:20.295
kama ule wa China?

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:24.352
Au tutaweza kutengeneza wa kwetu wa kipekee wa Africa.

00:03:24.376 --> 00:03:27.448
Ambao utakuwa wa kuridhisha na wa faida kwa maendeleo?

00:03:27.905 --> 00:03:29.594
Nina amini tunaweza.

00:03:29.992 --> 00:03:32.560
Nawajua Wa Africa ambao tayari wanaufanya.